{"tid":1660774,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大佬！幫下手都得掛？又話盡做！？","createTime":"2019-10-17T16:50:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-18T00:59:03.000Z","uid":268388,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"69e8b7c422a34f5815e5ef18e57659ba5a27febf","tid":1660774,"uid":268388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T16:50:48.000Z","msg":"今日係銅鑼灣見到好多手足幫手派1020傳單，但反應一般！<br />\n<br />\n我做過派傳單！我想講手足犧牲自己私人時間幫手宣傳，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">無論你自己知唔知1020活動都好，幫手接張傳單，同手足講一句：「加油！到時見！」。佢地信心會大增！起馬知道重有好多同路人互相支持！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n既然你已知道1020活動，咁接傳單黎做咩？請你將手上一張傳單傳俾身邊一個人！你都係傳一張姐，有幾難？咁都唔幫手？<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">請大家見到手足派文宣，一定要接，同手足講句加油！到時見！再將手上文宣傳俾身邊既人！一個一個傳開去！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6coHjRo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6coHjRo.png&h=6de941d9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GS1YCC8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGS1YCC8.png&h=f0d2e82b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4ef4ddf29e4b8185c29c33aa54b7e7b731d4f30b","tid":1660774,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T16:51:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jwJzHzo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjwJzHzo.jpg&h=eb217258&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"b034a6653f44207e8dc5497f7cf1696fe8408583","tid":1660774,"uid":77717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T16:51:36.000Z","msg":"全港十八區都要做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29780e8bc78dc7ebc8f5d7cff85898ef83a65d03","tid":1660774,"uid":82450,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T16:51:51.000Z","msg":"加油"},{"pid":"c166a644e45613aa1b35bf45030d00f3631b5328","tid":1660774,"u